Welcome to The TeX Catalogue Online, Hierarchical Index CTAN Edition. This Hierachical Index is based on the directory/folder structure of the CTAN nodes. Links at the leaves of the hierachy will take you to the corresponding item in The TeX Catalogue Online. The bold links will take you direct to the corresponding directory on the local CTAN.

Have a look at the Catalogue Preface for alternative ways of accessing the catalogue.

Icons associated with many entries in the catalogue allow you to:

  • view the directory on the local CTAN node
  • view documentation (possibly many)
  • view documentation in PDF format (requires acroread plugin)
  • jump to the package's home page
  • download a gzip'd tar file from a nearby CTAN node

Other icons simply provide further information about the package:

  • part of the teTeX distribution
  • available on the TeX Live CD ROM

The file CTAN:README.structure describes the purpose of each top level directory.
